We are thrilled to announce that DATA 2 KNOWLEDGE 2.0 was proudly presented by Dextra Labs, our titled sponsor, without whom the event would not have been possible. We extend our heartfelt gratitude to Dextra Labs for their invaluable support.
Dextra Labs, led by Vijay Agarwal and Sagar Doshi , both esteemed alumni of DJ Sanghvi College of Engineering, were not only instrumental as sponsors but also graced the event as judges. Their presence added immense value and insight to the proceedings.
With a commitment to excellence, Dextra Labs empowers businesses to thrive in the digital age through cutting-edge technologies, strategic insights, and unparalleled expertise.
We extend our heartfelt thanks to Dextra Labs for their invaluable support and presence at the event!!!

Grateful for the success of DATA TO KNOWLEDGE 2.0. 🙌 Wrapping up with this reel, showcasing the passion, teamwork, and innovation that made it possible. Cheers to all the participants, organisers and faculty members who were the life of this event ! 🚀
#datathon #starwars #hackathon #djsanghavicollege

A heartfelt thank you goes out to our incredible sponsors, Golden Oriole Education, for their unwavering support of the “Data 2 Knowledge 2.0” organized by DJ InIT.AI, the official AI Club of IT Department DJSCE! 🌟
Your belief in our vision and dedication to empowering the next generation of data enthusiasts is truly commendable. Not only did Golden Oriole Education generously sponsor our event, but they also went above and beyond by providing invaluable resources for our participants.
Special appreciation goes to Nishan Shetty from Golden Oriole Education, who conducted an enlightening seminar on abroad education, offering valuable insights to our attendees. Additionally, we extend our gratitude to Nishan for providing vouchers for the winners, enhancing the overall experience of the event.
Together, with the support of sponsors like Golden Oriole Education and individuals like Nishan Shetty, we are shaping the future of AI and knowledge dissemination! 🚀
